This is a project for Molcolm Concept Ltd
This project was created using the following technologies
 a. laravel
 b. mysql
 c. livewire
 
To replicate
1. run the mysql file in your localserver using the following parameters
  a. Database name = molcolm
  b. user name = root
  c. password = molcolm
  
 2.you can view the project by running it in insomia or postman
 a. to register a user
   url = localhost:8000/api/api_login
         name:
         email:
         password
         confirm_password
b. to login a user
       email:
       password
      note: if you successfully log in a user
       1. you get an access token
       2. you get to see how long the refresh token lasts
